{"tid":2079660,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"推細路 兇家長 椒亂噴  警狂拉14人 12歲網媒記者遭帶走","createTime":"2020-06-26T02:35:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T14:16:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b9846a2a35d5cc16e661d8a93d950c232c3432ad","tid":2079660,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T02:35:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200626/7XL7IJB26MIBZQJOANM32RNZDA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200626%2F7XL7IJB26MIBZQJOANM32RNZDA%2F&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2Ssg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=2d40ab32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200626%2F7XL7IJB26MIBZQJOANM32RNZDA%2F&h=d669792a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200626/7XL7IJB26MIBZQJOANM32RNZDA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n推細路 兇家長 椒亂噴 <br />\n警狂拉14人 12歲網媒記者遭帶走<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方執法標準及行動再受質疑！有網民號召昨天在元朗Yoho Mall舉行「和你shop」，半百防暴警以示威者非法集結為由，下午走入商場內驅散及截查巿民，有家長連同七歲男童入內購物，竟被防暴警驅趕，防暴警險推跌男童後，更爆粗辱罵家長及作勢舉胡椒噴霧，部份警員繼續有恃無恐，自行遮蓋行動編號，在無法得知其隸屬小隊組別下，多次亂射胡椒噴霧，擾攘六小時，警方共拘捕14人，另有一名12歲網媒記者被帶走。<br />\n<br />\n昨午1時許，<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n截查巿民。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hOe5fv_PF-hjwmqIRHVUQZrV0TU=/190x126/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KWLSTMXAGE4Y66LPHCJYSLQAUA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FhOe5fv_PF-hjwmqIRHVUQZrV0TU%3D%2F190x126%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKWLSTMXAGE4Y66LPHCJYSLQAUA.jpg&h=08520577&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【15:16】防暴警入商場驅趕時險推倒一名七歲男童，父親上前理論時，男警爆粗及作勢噴胡椒噴劑威嚇。<br />\n<br />\n【16:01】數名女子被警方用索帶反綁雙手拘捕。<br />\n【16:01】數名女子被警方用索帶反綁雙手拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/K5d-JxkbTO7sKZsEfvCFX6BFBcQ=/190x126/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TE2MCMM5EIK37TNCXQ4OSSM5HE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FK5d-JxkbTO7sKZsEfvCFX6BFBcQ%3D%2F190x126%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTE2MCMM5EIK37TNCXQ4OSSM5HE.jpg&h=48ebbdfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【16:01】警方共拘捕14人，一名12歲網媒記者則被帶走。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/CBY9t7K6y8tUcsGV18VscwlkVQw=/190x87/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/S5KO45H356D6LIKQVXPFHUH76A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FCBY9t7K6y8tUcsGV18VscwlkVQw%3D%2F190x87%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FS5KO45H356D6LIKQVXPFHUH76A.jpg&h=9c8a7631&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【19:00】一名手持美國隊長盾牌的男子高叫口號亦被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n貼「風林火山」徽章<br />\n<br />\n近2時，約50名防暴警及「速龍」警員突入商場，部份警員持胡椒球槍，並且架起橙色封鎖線清場，不少商舖隨即落閘，警員由地下登上二樓截查十多名巿民，並且沿途驅趕巿民離開，有一家三口持玩具甫走出玩具反斗城外不遠，其中七歲男童險被警員推跌，父親上前理論時，該名躁警反爆粗辱罵，又舉起胡椒噴霧作勢噴射，氣氛緊張。<br />\n<br />\n警員經截查後<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n即被警方無理截查。<br />\n<br />\n警方行動期間，有多名防暴警制服的頭肩位置都貼上「風林火山」，以及一個繡上「風」、「林」、「火」、「山」字眼、寫有「BRAVO」的徽章，另有警員再自行遮蓋小組行動編號，該外界無法得知警員身份及隸屬哪個警區小隊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pyYzgn9FrTn4bi0qNSJcLYNw2AU=/190x126/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ML2CXERAKD3DLJWCUZXNSBEX6U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpyYzgn9FrTn4bi0qNSJcLYNw2AU%3D%2F190x126%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FML2CXERAKD3DLJWCUZXNSBEX6U.jpg&h=52df6799&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大批防暴警在背心貼上風林火山徽章。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩議員中椒眼遭殃<br />\n<br />\n警員其後。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n晚上7時，其中一名手持美國隊長盾牌的男子繼續高叫「光復香港、香港獨立」口號時，數名便衣突然衝前制服，拘捕14人。未幾，警員亦陸續散去。<br />\n<br />\n元朗區議員林進及深水埗區議員何啟明，上前了解拘捕原因及要求便衣警出示委任證時，遭便衣警施射胡椒噴霧驅趕，多人中招，兩人事後無法睜開眼睛，需要義務救護員協助洗眼。林進指巿民在商場和平高叫口號，附近亦無人聚集，批評警方根本在打壓和平示威。"},{"pid":"56341efe0868a3a6393d4ff30805b9c95f1f8e66","tid":2079660,"uid":129348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T02:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hiC1UG3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhiC1UG3.jpg&h=23c973f1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zVJXs14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzVJXs14.jpg&h=f913e1d7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LvTwxtL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLvTwxtL.jpg&h=fa64d749&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【#71遊行 堅持五大訴求 反抗國安惡法】<br />\n<br />\n日期｜2020 年 7 月 1 日 星期三<br />\n集合地點｜維園集合<br />\n集合時間｜2PM<br />\n起步時間｜3PM<br />\n遊行終點｜金鐘添美道<br />\n*遊行正申請不反對通知書"},{"pid":"b09033b3de78e64b946a6a641903a04e56a5b144","tid":2079660,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T04:07:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"></span>"},{"pid":"44cad6bde26bac7e3d5546d6ae97315b851be07c","tid":2079660,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T04:19:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e0888a443f0bda2ef7b024ff13bf13fbe00a5bd","tid":2079660,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T06:11:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c76d75fdef3613f193a73f45a81166dae40262cf","tid":2079660,"uid":34343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T06:25:06.000Z","msg":"風林火山<br />\n朋比為奸"},{"pid":"f16b822efd13220a104181bacbdafbbe799ab085","tid":2079660,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:16:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}